<br>
Take a club (especially if you're going monk/imperial cult)unless you're dying to make a non-lethal character, in which case you'd be better off with a char that can debuff/drain fatigue. <br>
<br>
Been hearing some not so nice things about Unarmored too<br>
<br>
When you think monk, think medieval monk, not D&amp;D monk.<br>
